{
  "stem": "12674.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "So they-- the Red Cross came and they took them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And they took them to the children's home, and they made beautiful rooms with white muslin curtains-- not the-- nylon curtains, or the net curtains, and everything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And they, they, they were too stupid-- they were too stupid to see it, or maybe they didn't care about the Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "They believed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was absolute-- it was-- you know like when you go into, into like a, a house of horrors they paint all kinds of things, in the back there are all kinds of machinations and horrible things, but in the front it all looks like this and that?",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only fronts, like in the movies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They make fronts, and in back you have all kinds of garbage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were storefronts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people were told to stay inside the houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They only took them where they wanted to see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't take them to the side street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't take them to the street by the barracks where I lived, where the roads were not paved, and when it rained we walked ankle deep in mud.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I mean ankle deep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took them into the few things and they showed it to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they went home and they said that Hitler is not that bad to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They, they showed it, that film.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the film existed, and I was been trying for a long time to get myself something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I was never able to get that piece when I was, with the swimming scene.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you ever hear of anybody or you have any access to anybody with the swimming scene, it would be a lifetime dream realized if I could get just a second of that.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
